data.description: Amazing 1 1/2 story brick home with panoramic views of the river valley that you can enjoy from the full-width main floor deck and walk-out patio.  The main floor offers three bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms in addition to the updated kitchen and open living room/dining room area.  The second floor offers a large master suite, complete will full bath and more spectacular views.  The walkout basement features a great room with fireplace, laundry area, rec area and plenty of space for storage.  Don't forget the two-car attached garage!!  Recent updates include new exterior and storm doors, new garage door, new floors and updated main bathroom.  The deck has had new flooring and railing installed in addition to being re-sealed and painted.  Don't miss out on this great property and neighborhood.
